Query.CommandText:
SELECT h.SOPNUMBE, h.docamnt, h.SHIPMTHD, h.DOCDATE, h.CUSTNMBR, h.CUSTNAME, h.PYMTRMID, h.CSTPONBR, d.ITEMNMBR, rtrim(d.ITEMDESC) as ITEMDESC, d.UNITPRCE, d.XTNDPRCE, d.QUANTITY, d.ACTLSHIP, h.SOPTYPE, h.TAXAMNT,
h.ShipToName, h.ADDRESS1 as SADDRESS1, case when h.ADDRESS2='' then rtrim(h.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(h.state) + ' ' + h.zipcode else h.address2 end as SADDRESS2, case when h.address2 ='' then '' when h.address3 ='' and h.address2 ='' then rtrim(h.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(h.state) + ' ' + h.ZIPCODE when h.ADDRESS3 ='' then rtrim(h.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(h.STATE) + ' ' + h.ZIPCODE end as SADDRESS3, case when h.address2 <> '' and h.address3 <> '' then rtrim(h.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(h.state) + ' ' + h.ZIPCODe else '' end as SADDRESS4, d.LNITMSEQ, h.SUBTOTAL, h.FRTAMNT, a.ADDRESS1 as BADDRESS1, case when a.ADDRESS2='' then rtrim(a.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(a.state) + ' ' + a.ZIP else a.address2 end as BADDRESS2, case when a.address2 ='' then '' when a.address3 ='' and a.address2 ='' then rtrim(a.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(a.state) + ' ' + a.ZIP when a.address3 ='' then rtrim(a.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(a.state) + ' ' + a.ZIP end as BADDRESS3, case when a.address2 <> '' and a.address3 <> '' then rtrim(a.CITY) + ', ' + rtrim(a.state) + ' ' + a.ZIP else '' end as BADDRESS4, h.DUEDATE, h.ORDRDATE, p.date1, p.date2, p.date3, case when p.datepercent1 is null then 0 else p.datepercent1 end as datepercent1, case when p.datepercent2 is null then 0 else p.datepercent2 end as datepercent2, case when p.datepercent3 is null then 0 else p.datepercent3 end as datepercent3, c.CMMTTEXT, s.[first invoice date], s.[number of payments], DATEADD(weekday,30, s.[first invoice date]) as seconddate, DATEADD(weekday,60, s.[first invoice date]) as thirdate, rtrim(r.custclas) as custclas
FROM RM00102 a LEFT OUTER JOIN SOP10100 AS h ON a.ADRSCODE = h.PRBTADCD AND a.CUSTNMBR = h.CUSTNMBR RIGHT OUTER JOIN SOP10200 AS d ON h.SOPNUMBE = d.SOPNUMBE AND h.SOPTYPE = d.SOPTYPE LEFT OUTER JOIN SOP10106 AS c ON h.SOPTYPE = c.SOPTYPE AND h.SOPNUMBE = c.SOPNUMBE LEFT OUTER JOIN AddIn_SOPDiscountProgram p on h.MSTRNUMB = p.MSTRNUMB LEFT OUTER JOIN addin_splitterms s on h.sopnumbe = s.[sop number] left outer join rm00101 r on h.custnmbr = r.custnmbr
where d.quantity <> 0 and h.soptype=3 and (p.DiscountType=0 or p.DiscountType is null) and s.[fully paid] is null
